This is my second map!! There is a lot of advanced lighting in place in the halls and spawns. THERE IS LOTS OF FLASHING just to warn you. Its theme is a run down insane assylum. There are multiple weapon pickup points. Some secret teleporters are also in place!!! Well you should get a good fps and have lots of fun. WARNING: The map is very dark I AM AWARE OF THIS it is suppose to be like this to stay as an on-the-edge-of-your-seat map! Well have fun and there is NO buyzone. I might add a secret one in a later sersions if people want it. Well leave comments NOT FLAME !!! if you dont like it dont d.l it plz :) THANX

-*-SPECIAL THANX GOES OUT TO SHEEPRIDER FOR ALL HIS HELP-*-

-JARHEAD

p.s. the .NAV file is included in the RAR d.l

P.S.S the map is much brighter then the screenshots show :)
